nterval, although such work would\nclearly benefit from improved UV spectroscopy to more accurately determine\ntheir neutral hydrogen column densities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Apr 2014 19:30:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2015 20:07:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
